title: Bruce Springsteen on Songwriting.mp3
description:
Bruce Springsteen discusses his songwriting techniques, inspirations and influences, in an interview conducted at his New Jersey home.

Broadcast on: BBC Radio 2, 7:00pm Saturday 24th January
Duration: 60 minutes
Categories: Music, Classic Pop & Rock

The 'bonus', of course is that I inadvertently uploaded the unedited version rather the one I 'trimmed'. You get a couple of minutes of BBC news and stuff before the programme begins. Ah well, it'll no doubt qualify as history one day! Anyway, just skip the first couple of mins.
